===Magic===
Dragonstone jewellery can be enchanted using [[Lvl-5 Enchant]], requiring level 68 [[Magic]]. The spell requires 1 [[Cosmic rune]], 15 [[Earth rune]]s, 15 [[Water rune]]s and the piece of Dragonstone [[Jewellery]] that is to be enchanted. When enchanted and charged, dragonstone jewellery is currently the only other means of [[teleportation]] that works up to level 30 [[Wilderness]] aside from the [[royal seed pod]] and the [[slayer ring]].
