== Trivia ==
* In the [[Tower of Life]] quest, the player has to answer a question to the [[Homunculus]] about how dragons can breathe [[Dragonfire|fire]]. One of the answers suggests that this is done with the power of 'magical dragonstones.' The other answer states that it happens through the ignition of gas when the dragon exhales. It is possible that the ignition of dragonfire is mediated through some magical property of dragonstone crystals.

